        <abstract>
            <p>Has asked Hooker to sign the Wallace memorial and send it on to THH.</p> 
<p>Read splendid lecture by THH on evolution in the <hi rend="italic">Times</hi> ["On the application of the laws of evolution to the arrangement of the Vertebrata and more particularly of the Mammalia", <hi rend="italic">Proc. Zool. Soc. Lond.</hi> (1880): 649–62].</p> 
